You've also given me the perfect
ending because most of us use

00:47:04.250 --> 00:47:07.170
that windows and mirrors
metaphor, which has been

00:47:07.170 --> 00:47:09.380
so incredibly useful, right.

00:47:09.380 --> 00:47:12.710
And here with us today, we have
the originator of that phrase,

00:47:12.710 --> 00:47:14.200
Dr. Rudine Sims Bishop.

00:47:14.200 --> 00:47:17.510
If you want to come
stand up, Dr. Bishop.

