to introduce her.

00:56:38.510 --> 00:56:43.770
[ Applause ]

00:56:43.770 --> 00:56:48.060
Jacqueline is a four-time
Newbery honor medalist,

00:56:48.060 --> 00:56:50.470
a Coretta Scott King
book award winner,

00:56:50.470 --> 00:56:53.800
a former young poets laureate.

00:56:53.800 --> 00:56:56.840
