Books is proud

01:01:22.630 --> 01:01:25.490
to present its first
bookseller of the year award,

01:01:25.490 --> 01:01:28.180
a prize that was created
because our organization wanted

01:01:28.180 --> 01:01:32.190
to recognize the role that
booksellers have as drivers

01:01:32.190 --> 01:01:34.310
