cause these kinds of issues.

01:13:33.520 --> 01:13:36.330
And it's best for us to ask
ourselves some true questions,

01:13:36.330 --> 01:13:38.360
to really mind our own psyches.

01:13:38.360 --> 01:13:39.660
This book is not
about any child.

01:13:39.660 --> 01:13:41.290
This book is about you.

01:13:41.290 --> 01:13:42.590
You read the book.

01:13:42.590 --> 01:13:43.890
Whatever you think happens
to this kid at the end

01:13:43.890 --> 01:13:47.610
