seen and read, you must.

01:25:37.100 --> 01:25:40.080
Written by Debbi Chocolate.

01:25:40.080 --> 01:25:42.710
Eric is also the
author/illustrator

01:25:42.710 --> 01:25:47.790
of the Pura Belpre Illustrator
award winning Grandma's Gift.

01:25:47.790 --> 01:25:49.090
Born in Harlem.

01:25:49.090 --> 01:25:50.390
That's so funny.

01:25:50.390 --> 01:25:54.320
You know, people born in Harlem
are so the real thing to me.

01:25:54.320 --> 01:25:57.540
So I was always so
jealous of black people

01:25:57.540 --> 01:26:00.090
who were born in Harlem.

01:26:00.090 --> 01:26:03.340
He lives and works in
Hartsdale, New York,

01:26:03.340 --> 01:26:05.330
which has the same first
three letters as Harlem.

01:26:05.330 --> 01:26:08.850
So we'll give you pass on that.

01:26:08.850 --> 01:26:12.730
But his work is mind blowing,
and he is mind blowing.

01:26:12.730 --> 01:26:15.080
And I'm so glad to
share the stage with him

01:26:15.080 --> 01:26:17.510
and present him with this award.

01:26:17.510 --> 01:26:29.680
[ Applause ]

01:26:29.680 --> 01:26:30.980
&gt;&gt; Eric Velasquez: Wow.

01:26:30.980 --> 01:26:32.430
There is a lot of you in here.

01:26:32.430 --> 01:26:38.880
Okay. Well, I have my speech.

01:26:38.880 --> 01:26:44.060
Okay. I wanted to start with,
for those that didn't see,

01:26:44.060 --> 01:26:45.580
the video that I recorded

01:26:45.580 --> 01:26:50.480
for the We Need Diverse
Books Organization, my wish.

01:26:50.480 --> 01:26:53.540
And my wish is that
in my lifetime,

01:26:53.540 --> 01:26:57.890
we'll replace this word,
"diversity," especially

01:26:57.890 --> 01:27:01.630
in books, with the
word "normal."

01:27:01.630 --> 01:27:06.470
It's a simple concept, you know.

01:27:06.470 --> 01:27:09.340
Because diversity in my
house didn't really exist.

01:27:09.340 --> 01:27:11.540
I grew up in a Spanish-speaking
household,

01:27:11.540 --> 01:27:14.600
but we went to the movies
to see American films

01:27:14.600 --> 01:27:17.210
that spoke English, watch
Spanish speaking television,

01:27:17.210 --> 01:27:18.850
listen to salsa music,

01:27:18.850 --> 01:27:21.060
but we also listened
to the Temptations.

01:27:21.060 --> 01:27:25.170
So it was like, you
mean diversity is

01:27:25.170 --> 01:27:27.940
like everything,
but that's my life.

01:27:27.940 --> 01:27:33.350
So that's my wish for all
of you, lots of normal.

01:27:33.350 --> 01:27:38.220
Okay. Now to my thanks you-s.

01:27:38.220 --> 01:27:42.330
So I want to thank the We Need
Diverse Book Organization,

01:27:42.330 --> 01:27:47.700
as well as the Walter
Award judging committee,

01:27:48.760 --> 01:27:52.440
which is named after my
friend Walter Dean Myers.

01:27:52.440 --> 01:27:54.650
Thank you to Rubin
Pfeffer, my agent,

01:27:54.650 --> 01:27:55.950
